{"tid":2517160,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張建宗：反修例五大訢求 中央已聽取民意 透過國安法及選舉法來回應","createTime":"2021-05-05T07:02:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T07:26:40.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5b26502fcefea52b6ffbe11613d36f4ae0eddeb8","tid":2517160,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:02:10.000Z","msg":"張建宗指強化管治屬複雜工作 聽取及回應民意責無旁貸<br />\n<br />\n經民聯議員盧偉國提出書面質詢，引述有評論指政府處理反修例風波和疫情時，部分決定與社情民意脫節，可能與改組中策組有關。<br />\n<br />\n政務司司長張建宗引述行政長官林鄭月娥回覆指，過去兩年本港出現亂象，令特區政府施政舉步維艱，最根本原因是整體社會沒有全面貫徹落實「一國兩制」，亦有部分人的「一國」意識有待提升，加上別有用心的人刻意誤導大眾對中央及特區關係的了解。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗指出，強化管治屬複雜工作，管治者聽取和回應民意固然責無旁貸，但負責任的政府亦需平衡民意和政策及其他考慮，相信去年制定的《香港國安法》及今年新修訂的香港選舉制度，有助恢復社會穩定，亦提供有利環境讓特區政府改善施政，有助政府做好政策制訂及解說工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1589319-20210505.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1589319-20210505.htm&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn2Abrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=a0b3db90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1589319-20210505.htm&h=d95d7fe9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1589319-20210505.htm</a>"},{"pid":"aba0b6301fe3f5579c4e8874dd747c2d2c015bb8","tid":2517160,"uid":251732,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:02:49.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"62de154aff56ead55df2b6d7536587072147e40e","tid":2517160,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:03:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc97c0266480a3c266d40c120985f700d7324052","tid":2517160